# Note: crate-app_iOS/Info.plist is COMMITTED (a clean base with NO OAuth client id) so CI can build
# from a fresh checkout — it was previously gitignored, which broke `tauri ios build` in CI ("failed
# to parse plist ... NotFound"). Tauri merges the channel's OAuth redirect scheme (and background
# audio) from the gitignored src-tauri/Info.ios.plist at `tauri ios dev|build` time
# (scripts/write-ios-plist.mjs). A local build may re-merge that scheme back into Info.plist — do NOT
# commit that diff (it would put the client id in git).
